research_municipality_step.notes: Rowlett, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government. The Mayor and City Council are elected at-large. Blake Margolis stepped down as Mayor on January 7, 2025, and Jeff Winget became acting Mayor. Jeff Winget was subsequently elected Mayor in a special election on May 3, 2025. Council members serve in designated 'Places' which are not geographical divisions.
